    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183200/extras/c74fc5c5af38e376de70e152bc570f65.poster.avif?t=1754887808\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183200/extras/c74fc5c5af38e376de70e152bc570f65.webm?t=1754887808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183200/extras/c74fc5c5af38e376de70e152bc570f65.mp4?t=1754887808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「东方绯月传」是一款Roguelike卡牌构筑策略游戏。你将扮演红魔馆二小姐芙兰朵露·斯卡雷特，发起一场“绯月异变”，和其他幻想乡少女们结下“不打不相识”的珍贵友谊。游戏策略不仅限于攻击、防御、移动，合理地用好击退、分身，并有效应对独特的地图机关机制，让绯月再度降临于这片土地吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183200/extras/42e25e3ee5e439f906d257bd6590cb7d.avif?t=1754887808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183200/extras_big/42e25e3ee5e439f906d257bd6590cb7d.avif?t=1754887808 width=800 height=413 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+场独特的战斗，我们为每个角色都精心设计了战斗演出</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6幕各具特色的战斗场景，体验在幻想乡各处名胜运用策略进行战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10场Boss战斗，对抗掌握强力符卡的幻想乡少女们</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独属于芙兰朵露·斯卡雷特的卡牌构筑思路，200+可用卡牌</p></li></ul>",
